# Task 2: Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

## Objective

Analyze the cleaned Google Play Store dataset using interactive visualizations to identify trends and patterns.

## Tools & Technologies

* Python
* Jupyter Notebook
* Pandas
* Plotly

## Steps Performed

* Loaded the cleaned dataset.
* Performed exploratory data analysis.
* Created interactive visualizations using Plotly.
* Analyzed app categories, installs, ratings, reviews, and pricing.
* Identified key insights from the data.

## Output

Interactive charts and visual insights highlighting the overall performance of Google Play Store applications.

## Files Included

* Task2.ipynb
* Screenshots
* Visualization Outputs

